{"author":"Iso Tester","data":{"alias":"tepid-bus-pomp","description":"## Why\n\nThe B5 cutover defaulted verify.gate_engine to workflow, but the workflow PLAN-REVIEW verify/coach prompt steps fail on the LIVE path: the generic RunnerAgentStep supplies only {ticket_id, ticket_context, repo_path}, not the {{plan}} variable (nor the findings/surviving listing in instructions) the plan-review verifier/coach prompts require — the way bespoke pass2_verify/pass4_coach (src/rebar/llm/plan_review/passes.py) construct them via resolve_prompt({'plan': plan}) + a findings listing. So review-plan via the workflow engine degrades to INDETERMINATE. PR #42 flipped the default back to bespoke as a hotfix; this story completes the plumbing so workflow becomes a correct default again.\n\n## What\n\n- Supply {{plan}} to the workflow verify + coach prompt steps. Likely: make RunnerAgentStep (src/rebar/llm/workflow/runs.py) merge the step's with: string inputs into the resolve_prompt template variables, and have an op emit the plan text (extend plan_review_assemble_criteria or add an op) + the findings/surviving listing as instructions (reuse the bespoke listing builders from passes.py:pass2_verify/pass4_coach, extracted to a shared helper — no duplication).\n- Wire the plan + instructions into BOTH dynamic-verify arms (agentic + single-turn) and into coach_notes, in gates/plan-review.yaml.\n- Consider whether verify should batch (bespoke batches findings by 12) — document or implement.\n- ADD a LIVE smoke test (REBAR_MCP_ALLOW_LLM) that runs review-plan via the workflow engine on a real ticket and asserts a non-INDETERMINATE verdict — the offline parity harness can't catch this (canned agents bypass prompt resolution).\n- Once live-correct, re-default verify.gate_engine to workflow.\n\n## Acceptance Criteria\n\n- [ ] The workflow plan-review verify + coach steps resolve {{plan}} and receive the findings/surviving listing on the LIVE path (no 'undefined variable' failure).\n- [ ] A live review-plan via the workflow engine returns a real PASS/BLOCK verdict (not INDETERMINATE) and signs a byte-compatible attestation.\n- [ ] A live (gated) smoke test guards this so the offline blind spot can't recur.\n- [ ] verify.gate_engine default is flipped back to workflow.\n- [ ] make lint + full test suite pass.","id":"0408-e8e5-f8aa-4d70","parent_id":"72d5-79ec-9e2e-4a2b","priority":2,"tags":[],"ticket_type":"task","title":"Complete the workflow plan-review verify/coach LIVE plumbing ({{plan}} + findings), then re-default gate_engine to workflow"},"env_id":"ade0f2ef-51cc-45a2-bb97-c09846cd3df5","event_type":"CREATE","timestamp":1782505625488462001,"uuid":"3a17f053-a9ab-4913-93e4-1bc127d9ee37"}